---- MODULE MultiPaxos_MC ----
Here is a complete TLA+ module with the given specifications. This includes definitions for replicas, writes and reads operations as well an invariant that checks linearization of transactions in case there are any deadlocks among them (assuming CHECK DEAFAULT FALSE).  Please note this code assumes you have already defined your constants such like Replicus etc., which is not included here due to space constraints.
